        <h1>Добавление программ в Unity панель</h1>
        <p>
            2012-06-27
            
                <a href="/tags/unity">unity</a>
            
        </p>
        <p class="lead">На примере Sublime редактора:<br />
<br />
Создайте файл <b>sublime.desktop</b> в <b>~/.local/share/applications</b><br />
или в <b>/usr/share/applications</b> если нужно добавить для всех пользователей (в последнем случае нужны права root)<br />
<br />
Пример содержимого файла:<br />
<div class="codebox"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">Desktop</span> <span class="n">Entry</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">Name</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Sublime</span> <span class="n">Text</span> <span class="n">Editor</span> <span class="mf">2.0</span>
<span class="n">Comment</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Sublime</span> <span class="n">Text</span> <span class="n">Editor</span> <span class="mf">2.0</span>
<span class="n">Exec</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;/home/user/bin/sublime_text2/sublime_text&quot;</span> <span class="o">%</span><span class="n">F</span>
<span class="n">MimeType</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">plain</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="n">Terminal</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">false</span>
<span class="n">Type</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Application</span>
<span class="n">Icon</span><span class="o">=/</span><span class="n">home</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">user</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="nb">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">sublime_text2</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">Icon</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">48</span><span class="n">x48</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">sublime_text</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">png</span>
<span class="n">Categories</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">GNOME</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">GTK</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">Utility</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">TextEditor</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">Development</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">Utility</span><span class="p">;</span>
</pre></div>
</div><br />
После этого программа будет доступна в меню от куда её можно добавить на панель Unity.<br /></p>

